# UI/UX Design System & Guidelines

## Design Philosophy

### Core Principles
- **Minimalist & Clean**: Generous whitespace, simple color palette with one clear accent color
- **Trust & Professionalism**: Build user confidence through clean, professional interface
- **Focus & Clarity**: Hyper-focused dashboard with unambiguous actions
- **Accessibility**: Support for dark mode, keyboard navigation, screen readers
- **Mobile-First**: Responsive design that works seamlessly across all devices

### Design Inspiration
- **Linear** (https://linear.app): Gold standard for focused, efficient task-based UI
- **Vercel** (https://vercel.com/dashboard): Clean, information-rich dashboard with excellent dark mode
- **Craft** (https://www.craft.do): Beautiful, focused writing and reading experience
- **Stripe Dashboard** (https://dashboard.stripe.com): Masterclass in simple, intuitive forms and settings

